@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_adpfuu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp((tmp + 0.35 * v1 + 0.68)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(0.07)
    v2 = 0.92
    v2 = wp.exp(v0)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.51 * v2 + 0.48)))
    tmp = 0.42
    data[tid] = v0
